title: Tim Tebow Just Became Mia Khalifa's Latest Trolling Victim
text:
Mia Khalifa Trolls Tim Tebow Over His Weird AF Guacamole Lunch © instagram.com/notthefakemiakhalifa Mia Khalifa Trolls Tim Tebow Over His Weird AF Guacamole Lunch Trending News: Tim Tebow Is Mia Khalifa's Latest Trolling Victim Shares Long Story Short 
From porn to trolling, Mia Khalifa is pretty much amazing at everything she does. And Tim Tebow has an unhealthy love for guacamole. Long Story 
If we need to tell you that Mia Khalifa used to be one of THE biggest names in porn, we have a problem. But there’s no time to address it now because the XXX superstar turned Queen Troll (who most recently spoke out about the inauguration ) and Boob Educator (here’s why having big breast sucks , in case you were wondering) has unleashed her wrath on Tim Tebow and it’s glorious. 
He may be an NFL great and one of the New York Mets’ most talked about new players , but Mia Khalifa couldn’t be less impressed by any of that because, well, homie doesn’t know how to eat guacamole. When For The Win sports writer Steven Ruiz posted a photo of Tim "sitting around eating guacamole straight out of a container", it immediately raised all the Internet eyebrows. Just Tim Tebow sitting around eating guacamole straight out of a container pic.twitter.com/xmHLWTtPmj — Steven Ruiz (@theStevenRuiz) February 3, 2017 
What did Mia think? She wasn't exactly into it... WHATTTT THE ACTUAL FUCK https://t.co/dliTipkbTv — Mia Khalifa (@miakhalifa) February 4, 2017 
There are two lessons to be learned here, folks. 1) Tim Tebow has an unhealthy love for the Super Bowl party staple and someone reeeeally needs to tell him that guac belongs on a delicious vessel, like a bagel or a chip or anything that's not a spoon and 2) If there's someone worth trolling in the sports world, Mia Khalifa should be called ASAP. You know, sort of like Ghostbusters, but way hotter. Own The Conversation 
But seriously: WTF is Tim Tebow doing? Disrupt Your Feed 
ESPN, please hire Mia Khalifa as a sports commentator. Drop This Fact 
Mia previously trolled Ole Miss quarterback Chad Kelly like there was no tomorrow. Today's Hottest Deals
